:Def4: ((( len it ) = ( len A ) & ( width it ) = ( width B )) & (for i holds (for j holds ([ i,j ] in ( Indices it ) implies ( it * (i,j) ) = ( ( Line (A,i) ) "*" ( Col (B,j) ) )))));
existence
proof
deffunc F(Nat,Nat) = ( ( Line (A,$1) ) "*" ( Col (B,$2) ) );
consider M being (Matrix of ( len A ),( width B ),K) such that A2: (for i holds (for j holds ([ i,j ] in ( Indices M ) implies ( M * (i,j) ) = F(i,j)))) from MATRIX_1:sch 1;
take M;
now
per cases ;
case ( len A ) > ( 0 );
hence (( len M ) = ( len A ) & ( width M ) = ( width B )) by MATRIX_1:23;
end;
case A3: ( len A ) = ( 0 );
then ( len B ) = ( 0 ) by A1,MATRIX_1:def 3;
then A4: ( width B ) = ( 0 ) by MATRIX_1:def 3;
( len M ) = ( 0 ) by A3,MATRIX_1:25;
hence (( len M ) = ( len A ) & ( width M ) = ( width B )) by A3,A4,MATRIX_1:def 3;
end;
end;
hence thesis by A2;
end;
uniqueness
proof
